		{
			dependencies: ["127DAB9080BE7D68"]
			description: [
				"You can get certain &6EVs&r by defeating certain Pokémon in fights. "
				""
				"Pidgey for example has a high base Speed stat. Your Pokémon will gain 1 Speed EV after beating each Pidgey. "
				""
				"For every 4 EV points, your total stat will be increased by 1. Along with the total EV cap of &6510&r, you can only have &6252&r EV in one specific stat. "
				""
				"For EV training, you generally want to dedicate &6252&r EV to Speed and &6252&r to Atk (or Special Atk) and dump 4 into whichever."
			]
