		{
			dependencies: ["127DAB9080BE7D68"]
			description: [
				"The maximum &6IVs&r a Pokémon can have for each stat is 31 and the minimum is 0."
				""
				"Generally, you want to have the highest IVs possible to make your Pokémon reach its absolute limit."
				""
				"In most situations, you want Pokémon with high IVs. However, the stats in which the IVs are distributed in also matter. "
				""
				"For example, physical attackers will want to have high &6HP&r, &6Attack&r, &6Defence&r, &6Special Defence&r, and &6Speed&r. Special Attack does not matter for physical attackers."
